Excited to premiere ‘bodybound’ tonight… a new creation in collaboration with @so.born.art for @staatstheaterkassel ‘Let’s Talk About Bodies in Space’… a research project featuring 7 original works by the dancers of @tanzkassel

What a gift It has been to dive into this process and share the stage with you @so.born.art 🤍

Only two more chances to catch our piece ‘bodybound’ for ‘Let’s Talk About: Bodies In Space’ alongside 5 original works by the dancers of @tanzkassel 💫 

Tonight 20:15 @staatstheaterkassel TiF
Final performance 28/05

“whose bones have been entangled by time” by @yannis.brsst 🦴 

Sad to be leaving this piece behind after tomorrow night.. what a beautiful journey It has been creating, collaborating and growing throughout this process alongside this team.

Final performance of ‘Bodies in Space’ tomorrow 20:15 @staatstheaterkassel TiF 

📷 @buehnenlicht 
👕 @ma.the.wa 
🎵 @dario_wil 
🎭 @eline_vey

Tonight is the last show of ‘Dharma’ by Ashley Lobo and my final performance with @tanzkassel @staatstheaterkassel ✨ 

Thank you to everyone who has made these two seasons truly unforgettable… It has been a gift to dance and work alongside such beautiful people and I will cherish these moments and memories 5eva!
